&lt;h3 id=&#34;istio-virtual-service&#34;&gt;Istio virtual service&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A virtual service helps in connecting the gateway to the Kubernetes service. It is a set of rules for routing traffic based on the match criteria for a specific protocol. If the traffic matches the criteria, then it will be sent to a named destination service.&lt;/p&gt;
